title: Whistlefritz Spanish for Beginners
description:
This award-winning Spanish immersion program gives children an ideal introduction to Spanish, through skits, dance, song, and play.  Accompanied by their young friends and puppet pals, kids learn the parts of the body, clothing, numbers, animals, sounds and more.

Includes beloved Spanish-language folksongs Los Pollitos and Vengan a Ver Mi Granja.  Designed for ages 2-5.
